    "text": "you see what's going on in DC today? feels like every day Nashville writes a sadder song and Washington tries to one-up it 😂 Derek had the radio on in the booth and we all just kinda went quiet mid-take"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-20T19:27:21+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000001",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "19",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000000",
    "retweet_count": "3",
    "text": "right?? had to put my phone down just to eat lunch. at least your whole job is literally processing feelings for a living lol"
  },
  {
