    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "8",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000001",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "Mamá called before the session — said Abuelita's had the news on all morning. when Elena Morales is glued to the TV you know it's a bad one"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-19T21:41:01+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000003",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "52",
    "quote_count": "3",
    "reply_count": "7",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000002",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "ok doña Elena is officially the barometer I didn't know I needed 😭 if she's worried we should ALL be worried"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-18T15:02:11+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000004",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "44",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "6",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000003",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "writing tip nobody asked for: keep the voice memo even when the melody is trash. the trash one from March is half of the song Derek and I tracked this week. nothing is wasted"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-17T22:48:53+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000005",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "61",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "9",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000004",
    "retweet_count": "4",
    "text": "Carly Thornton's record hitting 42 on country radio with a song I co-wrote still doesn't feel real. heard it at a gas station in San Antonio over Christmas and just stood there like an idiot"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:31:20+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000006",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "38",
    "quote_count": "2",
    "reply_count": "4",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000005",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "Tejano legends don't get talked about enough in this town. Flaco Jimenez forgot more about phrasing than half of Music Row will ever learn. put some respect on the accordion"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-15T13:09:44+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000007",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "27",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000006",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "session backup singing pays the rent and I will defend it forever. you learn more about blend and dynamics standing behind somebody else's mic than you ever do out front"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-14T11:25:07+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000008",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "112",
    "quote_count": "5",
    "reply_count": "21",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000007",
    "retweet_count": "3",
    "text": "34 today. spent it the right way: pozole on the stove, a half finished song on the table, and Mamá on speaker telling me I still don't eat enough. grateful"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-13T20:14:38+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000009",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "49",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "7",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000008",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "three of five tracked on the EP. Derek says the b-side is the strongest thing I've cut. I think he says that about every song to keep me coming back, and it works every time"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-12T16:40:55+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000010",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "33",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "5",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000009",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "cowrite ran long, totally worth it. Vanessa set me up with a writer who hears harmony the way I do. left with two thirds of something real and a hook I couldn't shake on the Uber home"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
