    "id": "2000000000000000011",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "58",
    "quote_count": "2",
    "reply_count": "8",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000010",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "Selena would have been the biggest crossover this country town ever saw and y'all aren't ready to admit it. put 'Como La Flor' on a steel guitar and watch what happens"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-10T19:55:41+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000012",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "41",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "6",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000011",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "Riverstone Listening Room tonight was the kind of quiet where you can hear a songwriter's hands shake. that's the good stuff. lower Broadway can keep the cover bands"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
    "created_at": "2025-12-09T14:03:29+00:00",
    "id": "2000000000000000013",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "36",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "4",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000012",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "got burned by a cowriter twice early on so now every lyric draft is timestamped before it leaves my kitchen. protect your work. nobody else is going to do it for you"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1000000000000000001",
