    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000013",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "7:30am yoga at Sunrise Flow then straight to Copperline. somewhere between downward dog and the first take is where I do my best thinking. don't ask me to explain it"
