    "reply_count": "5",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000014",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "Sunday means tamales and the whole family on the phone at once. I make them the way Abuelita taught me even when it's just me and the JBL speaker in an East Nashville kitchen"
