    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2000000000000000015",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "found a pair of 1970s Western boots at an estate sale that fit like they were waiting for me. that's 14 pairs now. Keisha says I have a problem. Keisha is correct and I do not care"
